	<text id="0">
		<p>
			You spend a first fruitless day looking for a place with this name. After this, for every day that 
			passes, you can <a href="http://domulti:3">roll one die</a>. When you roll a 5 or 6, you can continue.
			If you wish, you can increase the number rolled on the die by 1 by spending a point of Luck. If you
			tire of this, you can <a href="http://link:272">try looking for a person named Endimion</a> or
			<a href="http://link:226">ask questions about the grey-robed men</a>, if you haven't already done this.
		</p>
